Game/Life/Infinite::Board $Revision: 0.01 $
======================

Game::Life::Infinite::Board is a Perl module to implement 
the well known Conway's Game of Life on an infinite board (grid).
Different than the standard Die/Breed rules can be passed as
parameters on the creation of the grid or anytime later.
Oscilating formations of any period can be detected.
More information can be found in the perldoc for this module.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires:

     Perl 5.10.1
     Time::HiRes

